<figcaption>a test o duotone risoprint</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitledggg_-1.png" data-size="502x502"><img loading="lazy" src="https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitledggg_-1-thumbnail.webp" alt="test of mono color risoprint with strong dithering" width="502" height="502"></a>
